convenient for everyone.

00:04:17.680 --> 00:04:19.315
For everyone's convenience, huh?

00:04:19.760 --> 00:04:21.239
The moment Meiqi went abroad,

00:04:21.440 --> 00:04:23.137
that streetlight stopped working.

00:04:24.279 --> 00:04:27.159
That must've been
because of the heavy rain.

00:04:29.039 --> 00:04:31.239
More like a storm in your heart.

00:04:35.359 --> 00:04:36.640
Now that Meiqi's back,

00:04:36.919 --> 00:04:38.039
