I...

00:05:03.120 --> 00:05:04.239
I don't know how to drive.

00:05:09.399 --> 00:05:09.919
You...

00:05:10.137 --> 00:05:12.080
How exactly are you
going to get her home?

00:05:13.120 --> 00:05:14.880
I have...

00:05:14.960 --> 00:05:15.359
I...

00:05:15.599 --> 00:05:16.799
