No wonder
you still don't have a girlfriend.

00:05:26.200 --> 00:05:26.560
What?

00:05:26.640 --> 00:05:28.360
Because I don't
have a driver's license?

00:05:30.320 --> 00:05:31.640
Look at him.

00:05:32.080 --> 00:05:32.760
Chen!

00:05:34.279 --> 00:05:35.239
Zhidong!

00:05:35.239 --> 00:05:36.200
Over here!

00:05:37.440 --> 00:05:38.080
Mr. Hu?

00:05:38.560 --> 00:05:39.349
Mr. Hu.

00:05:39.350 --> 00:05:40.071
Long time no see.

00:05:40.071 --> 00:05:40.915
It's been a while.

00:05:41.399 --> 00:05:42.399
We'll get going then.

00:05:43.120 --> 00:05:44.159
Meiqi's in your care.

00:05:45.799 --> 00:05:47.320
Princess, your carriage awaits.

00:05:47.320 --> 00:05:48.960
Let's go.

00:05:49.680 --> 00:05:51.359
Why didn't you ride your bike today?

00:05:51.520 --> 00:05:52.799
Well, you had some drinks,

00:05:53.359 --> 00:05:54.159
so we'll take a cab.

00:05:54.880 --> 00:05:56.799
I'll call a premium ride tonight.

00:06:10.039 --> 00:06:11.399
I've never been on an e-scooter.

00:06:12.120 --> 00:06:13.399
The breeze feels so nice.

00:06:13.680 --> 00:06:14.359
Yeah?

00:06:15.200 --> 00:06:17.120
If you want,

00:06:17.520 --> 00:06:18.960
I can take you every day.

00:06:20.226 --> 00:06:21.640
Your school is in the old town.

00:06:21.640 --> 00:06:22.869
I live in the new district.

00:06:22.870 --> 00:06:23.582
That's really far.

00:06:24.680 --> 00:06:25.880
So what?

00:06:25.880 --> 00:06:27.200
We'll just leave earlier.

00:06:29.479 --> 00:06:31.159
Look, that's Nanzhou University.

00:06:31.159 --> 00:06:39.960
(Nanzhou University)

00:06:40.000 --> 00:06:42.239
Look, that's Nanzhou University.

00:06:44.200 --> 00:06:46.960
Last year,
seven of my students got in here.

00:06:47.159 --> 00:06:48.080
Wow, that's impressive.

00:06:50.200 --> 00:06:50.839
Hu Gang.

00:06:51.479 --> 00:06:53.120
You had such good grades back then.

00:06:53.150 --> 00:06:54.626
Why did you go to a normal school?

00:06:57.599 --> 00:06:58.520
I'm not like you.

00:06:58.799 --> 00:07:00.440
You've seen a lot since you were little.

00:07:01.039 --> 00:07:02.359
As for me,

00:07:02.919 --> 00:07:04.440
I've only ever been to Thailand,

00:07:04.680 --> 00:07:06.160
and that was with a tour group.

00:07:08.000 --> 00:07:10.839
All I knew growing up was
how to study and take exams.

00:07:11.560 --> 00:07:14.000
Well, I actually enjoy doing exercises.

00:07:14.399 --> 00:07:16.120
When it came time to pick a major,

00:07:16.440 --> 00:07:17.799
I only picked education schools.

00:07:18.910 --> 00:07:20.360
After I graduated from college,

00:07:20.440 --> 00:07:23.599
I decided to go back
and teach at Nanzhou High School.

00:07:24.560 --> 00:07:27.159
Everything there just felt so familiar.

00:07:27.599 --> 00:07:29.760
Even the volume of the class bells was

00:07:29.760 --> 00:07:30.520
the same as before.

00:07:32.680 --> 00:07:33.440
That's nice.

00:07:33.671 --> 00:07:34.790
You are shaping young minds

00:07:35.399 --> 00:07:36.560
as a great teacher.

00:07:37.640 --> 00:07:38.760
There's just one downside.

00:07:39.120 --> 00:07:40.320
My students drive me crazy.

00:07:40.719 --> 00:07:42.200
I've developed nodules all over.

00:07:42.479 --> 00:07:44.479
One day it's a lung nodule,

00:07:44.479 --> 00:07:46.039
the next it's a thyroid one.

00:07:46.093 --> 00:07:48.030
Not a single one of them
gives me peace of mind.

00:07:48.030 --> 00:07:49.648
They're more mischievous than we were.

00:07:53.239 --> 00:07:54.120
It's getting chilly.

00:07:54.200 --> 00:07:55.000
Let's head back.

00:08:03.399 --> 00:08:04.799
Here, put this on.

00:08:07.560 --> 00:08:08.479
Fits pretty well.

00:08:09.560 --> 00:08:10.640
Keeping warm in the cold.

00:08:10.719 --> 00:08:11.719
This is easy.

00:08:12.799 --> 00:08:13.279
Come on.

00:08:13.279 --> 00:08:13.919
Let's go.

00:08:16.919 --> 00:08:17.560
Sis.

00:08:18.239 --> 00:08:19.589
You can't always wait for me

00:08:19.590 --> 00:08:20.819
to come downstairs with you.

00:08:20.820 --> 00:08:22.300
You need to move around more yourself.

00:08:22.360 --> 00:08:24.537
Otherwise, how can you
keep up with your grandson?

00:08:26.359 --> 00:08:27.680
I just get scared sometimes.

00:08:28.399 --> 00:08:30.839
I'm afraid people will ask
where my son went.

00:08:33.960 --> 00:08:35.440
Here, go on.

00:08:37.960 --> 00:08:38.960
Hey, isn't that Meiqi?

00:08:39.639 --> 00:08:41.359
Why is she coming back on an e-scooter?

00:08:42.759 --> 00:08:44.200
Yeah, pull it down a little.

00:08:44.200 --> 00:08:44.639
That's it.

00:08:44.639 --> 00:08:45.200
Got it.

00:08:47.560 --> 00:08:48.519
Thanks for today.

00:08:50.479 --> 00:08:51.719
Get home safe, alright?

00:08:52.479 --> 00:08:53.160
Bye.

00:08:56.200 --> 00:08:57.479
Meiqi!

00:08:58.920 --> 00:09:00.839
Since you didn't drive back,

00:09:01.200 --> 00:09:03.719
how about I pick you up
tomorrow morning?

00:09:03.719 --> 00:09:05.440
No need. It's easy to grab a cab.

00:09:05.440 --> 00:09:06.080
Bye.

00:09:17.639 --> 00:09:18.680
Excuse me, sir.

00:09:18.960 --> 00:09:20.359
You can't park your car here.

00:09:20.800 --> 00:09:21.599
Sorry.

00:09:21.599 --> 00:09:22.639
I'll move right away.

00:09:41.080 --> 00:09:42.040
Auntie's here.

00:10:02.719 --> 00:10:03.440
What's wrong?

00:10:04.639 --> 00:10:05.719
What are you two up to?

00:10:11.839 --> 00:10:12.560
Meiqi,

00:10:12.960 --> 00:10:15.160
